# Brute Force Detection Query

This query identifies potential brute-force login attempts against the honeypot by detecting excessive failed login attempts within a short time window.

Event ID 4625 represents failed Windows authentication attempts.

SecurityEvent
| where EventID == 4625
| summarize FailedAttempts = count() by IPAddress, Account, bin(TimeGenerated, 5m)
| where FailedAttempts > 10
